# BODYiQ Product Principles

## Guiding principle
Be the "truth and light." Only recommend what a user genuinely needs — no upselling for upselling's sake.

## Strategic context
Wellness app for payors (UHC, BCBS) to keep beneficiaries out of hospitals and support healthy aging in place.

## Core principles
- **Simplicity first** — dumb simple by default; complexity is opt-in
- **Tiered effort** — user picks engagement level at signup (light / moderate / high-touch)
- **No notification fatigue** — reminder frequency is user-controlled
- **Voice everywhere** — voice input throughout (Phase 2+ wiring)
- **Bilingual** — English at launch; Spanish in a later phase

## Mobile-first
This repo is the **mobile app** (Expo/React Native), not the marketing website.

## Commerce ethics
Integrate BODYiQ products along user paths only when relevant to their plan. Never dark-pattern or pressure purchases.
